Title: toIntervalNanosecond
Description: Returns an interval of n nanoseconds of data type IntervalNanosecond.
n — Number of nanoseconds. Integer numbers or string representations thereof, and float numbers. (U)Int*/Float*/String.
Examples: WITH    toDateTime('2024-06-15') AS date,    toIntervalNanosecond(30) AS interval_to_nanosecondsSELECT date + interval_to_nanoseconds AS result
